INSERT INTO COREAPPS.DEPENDENTS_PHONE (
    ID,
    SUBS_ID,
    HOF_ID,
    PHONE_NUMBER,
    CREATED_DATE,
    FLG_ENABLE
)
SELECT DEPENDENTS_PHONE_SEQ.NEXTVAL,
{{ dep_table.selectedRow.ID }},   -- hof id
       {{ subsTable.selectedRow.ID }},   -- subscriber id
       '{{ PhoneInput1.dialCode }}{{ PhoneInput1.text }}', -- phone
       SYSDATE,
       1
FROM dual
WHERE NOT EXISTS (
    SELECT 1
    FROM COREAPPS.DEPENDENTS_PHONE dp
    WHERE dp.SUBS_ID = {{ subsTable.selectedRow.ID }}
)
